choices.choice:
Use the AddDrives API method.
This method has the following input parameter:
NameDescriptionTypeDefault value Required 
drivesInformation about each drive to be added to the cluster. Possible values:
driveID: The ID of the drive to add (integer).
type: The type of drive to add (string). Valid values are "slice", "block", or "volume". If omitted, the system assigns the correct type.JSON object arrayNoneYes (type is optional)
Here is a request example:{
  "id": 1,
  "method": "AddDrives",
  "params": {
    "drives": [
      {
        "driveID": 1,
        "type": "slice"
      },
      {
        "driveID": 2,
        "type": "block"
      },
      {
        "driveID": 3,
        "type": "block"
      }
    ]
  }
}
For more information about this API method, see here.
